, blir v\u00e5penet beslaglagt og personen blir anmeldt, sier stasjonssjef Arve Nordtvedt."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "857157443316ec708fa8e14c075a48b8da13e6ccd8d96a762910a8b0d6773c77"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-01T17:51:12.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Det er ikke bare godt hum\u00f8r folk tar med seg p\u00e5 byturen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article8816039.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/beslag%20001.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/a9e67feee7fce9e138511595235422ea1e2f8b38.jpg?591b0373"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Politiet fant dette p\u00e5 byen i helga -adressa.no", "Forebyggende tiltak", "Beslag og anmeldelse"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "a9e67feee7fce9e138511595235422ea1e2f8b38"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["politiet", "personer", "v\u00e5pen", "politiet fant", "byen"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["sentrum", "politiloven"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "arve nordtvedt"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/trondheim"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article8816039.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/beslag%20001.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value"